/movieSearch?starId=20731&theaterId=42331|title=Adult Movie Database|publisher=AMVDB|date=|access-date=2012-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317151949/http://www.amvdb.com/dispatcher/movieSearch?starId=20731&theaterId=42331|archive-date=March 17, 2012|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n== Early life ==\nSage grew up in a middle class household with her parents, who were both teachers. She remembers wanting to work in the [[adult entertainment industry]] as early as 14 years old.<ref name=\"ishootporn\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ishootporn.com/1603/porno-interview-49-sinn-sage/ |title=I Shoot Porn|publisher=I Shoot Porn|date=September 9, 2008|accessdate=2012-07-07}}</ref> Before entering the industry, she worked at a [[video game store]], at [[Hot Topic]], and [[waitress]]ed at an [[Olive Garden]] restaurant.<ref name=\"adultdvdtalk\"/>\n\n== Career ==\n\nAccording to Sage, she began her career in adult entertainment in 2002 with a few photo shoots and exotic dancing. after visiting the [[AVN Adult Entertainment Expo|AVN Expo]] in 2003, she started performing in videos as well.<ref name=\"adultdvdtalk\">{{cite web | url=http://interviews.adultdvdtalk.com/sinn-sage/ | title= Captain Jack interviews Sinn Sage |publisher= AdultDVDTalk.com|date= July 6, 2014|accessdate= March 27, 2015}}</ref> Despite not working with males for her entire career, she began webcamming and performing scenes with her husband in 2013. \nSage is now a producer as well as performer, and she and her husband produce custom videos and content for their website, sinn-sage.com, as well as full-length films under the banner Sinn Sage Studios distributed by Trouble Films.\n\n== Personal life ==\nOn November 21, 2015, after 4 years of dating, Sage wed her boyfriend, porn actor Drake ManO'War.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/sinnsage/status/670018822036922368 |title=Sinn Sage on Twitter|publisher=Twitter|accessdate=October 18, 2016}}</ref>{{additional citation needed|date=February 2020}}\n \nSage describes herself as an [[anti-theist]].<ref>https://www.twitter.com/sinnsage/status/926639675569184768</ref>  Despite almost exclusively shooting [[lesbian pornography|lesbian porn]], she ultimately identifies as queer and pansexual.<ref name=\"adultdvdtalk\"/>\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=wikitable width=75%\n|-\n!width=7%|Year\n!width=7%|Ceremony\n!\n!width=42%|Category\n!width=46%|Work\n!width=8%|Result\n|-\n|align=center|[[27th AVN Awards|2010]]\n|rowspan=8 align=center|[[AVN Award|AVN]]\n|\n|Best All-Girl Group Sex Scene<ref name=\"avnnom2010\">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304153045/http://avnawards.avn.com/nominees|title=AVN \u2013 2010 AVN Awards Show \u2013 2010 Nominees|work=[[AVN (magazine)|AVN]]|publisher=[[AVN Media Network]]|archivedate=March 4, 2010|url=http://avnawards.avn.com/nominees|accessdate=January 25, 2015}}</ref>\n|''Belladonna's Road Trip: Cabin Fever'' <small>(shared with Julie Night, [[Bobbi Starr]], Ava Rose, Rucca Paige, [[Alexis Texas]] and Alexa Jordan)</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=3 align=center|[[29th AVN Awards|2012]]<ref name=\"avnnom2012\">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123135604/http://avnawards.avn.com/2012_AVN_Awards_nominations.pdf|title=AVN AWARDS 2012 \u2013 NOMINATIONS|work=AVN|publisher=AVN Media Network|archivedate=January 23, 2013|url=http://avnawards.avn.com/2012_AVN_Awards_nominations.pdf|accessdate=January 25, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|rowspan=2|Best All-Girl Group Scene\n|''Belladonna: Sexual Explorer'' <small>(shared with [[Belladonna (actress)|Belladonna]] and Sarah Shevon)</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|\n|''Party of Feet 3'' <small>(shared with Ann Marie Rios, Alexis Texas and Kristina Rose)</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|\n|Most Outrageous Sex Scene\n|''Party of Feet 3'' \u2013 Scene: \"Feet, Pray, Love\" <small>(shared with Ann Marie Rios, Alexis Texas and Kristina Rose)</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2 align=center|[[30th AVN Awards|2013]]\n|\n|B