{"title_page": "Angelos Vertzos", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|      name      = Angelos Vertzos\n|           image =\n|          height = {{height|m=1.75}}\n|     birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1983|05|27}}\n| birth_place = [[Athens]], Greece\n| currentclub = [[Trikala F.C.|Trikala]]\n|      clubnumber = 5\n|        position = [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|Centre-back]]\n|          years1 = 2002\u20132005\n|          clubs1 = [[Acharnaikos F.C.|Acharnaikos]]\n|           caps1 = 71\n|          goals1 = 0\n|          years2 = 2005\n|          clubs2 = [[Paniliakos F.C.|Paniliakos]]\n|           caps2 = 2\n|          goals2 = 0\n|          years3 = 2005\u20132006\n|          clubs3 = [[Acharnaikos F.C.|Acharnaikos]]\n|           caps3 = 29\n|          goals3 = 2\n|          years4 = 2006\u20132007\n|          clubs4 = [[Proodeftiki F.C.|Proodeftiki]]\n|           caps4 = 31\n|          goals4 = 0\n|          years5 = 2007\u20132008\n|          clubs5 = [[Agios Dimitrios F.C.|Agios Dimitrios]]\n|           caps5 = 5\n|          goals5 = 0\n|          years6 = 2008\u20132010\n|          clubs6 = [[Veria F.C.|Veria]]\n|           caps6 = 46\n|          goals6 = 0\n|          years7 = 2010\u20132012\n|          clubs7 = [[Doxa Drama F.C.|Doxa Drama]]\n|           caps7 = 41\n|          goals7 = 1 \n|          years8 = 2012\u20132013\n|          clubs8 = [[Niki Volou]]\n|           caps8 = 36\n|          goals8 = 2 \n|          years9 = 2013\u20132014\n|          clubs9 = [[Apollon Smyrnis F.C.|Apollon Smyrnis]]\n|           caps9 = 6\n|          goals9 = 0 \n|          years10 = 2014\u20132015\n|          clubs10 = [[Veria F.C.|Veria]]\n|           caps10 = 38\n|          goals10 = 0\n|          years11 = 2015\u20132016\n|          clubs11 = [[AE Larissa FC|AEL]]\n|           caps11 = 24\n|          goals11 = 0\n|          years12 = 2016\u20132018\n|          clubs12 = [[Trikala F.C.|Trikala]]\n|           caps12 = 56\n|          goals12 = 2\n|          years13 = 2018\n|          clubs13 = [[PAE Kerkyra|Kerkyra]]\n|           caps13 = 9\n|          goals13 = 0\n|          years14 = 2019\n|          clubs14 = [[Diagoras F.C.|Diagoras]]\n|           caps14 = 9\n|          goals14 = 0\n|          years15 = 2019\u2013\n|          clubs15 = [[Trikala F.C.|Trikala]]\n|           caps15 = 0\n|          goals15 = 0\n|          pcupdate = 25 December 2018 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Angelis Vertzos''' ({{lang-el|\u0386\u03b3\u03b3\u03b5\u03bb\u03bf\u03c2 \u0392\u03ad\u03c1\u03c4\u03b6\u03bf\u03c2}}, born 27 May 1983) is a Greek professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|centre-back]] for [[Football League (Greece)|Football League]] club [[Trikala F.C.|Trikala]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=crimsonscorer.gr|title=\u0391.\u0395.\u039b.: \u0391\u03bd\u03b1\u03ba\u03bf\u03af\u03bd\u03c9\u03c3\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b5\u03c4\u03b1\u03b3\u03c1\u03b1\u03c6\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae \u03c4\u03c1\u03b9\u03ac\u03b4\u03b1! (pics) |url=http://www.crimsonscorer.gr/index.php/ael/item/7223-ael-anakoinose-metagrafiki-triada-pics.html|accessdate=2015-07-21}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|publisher=aelfc.gr|title=\u039b\u03cd\u03c3\u03b7 \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u03c3\u03c5\u03bd\u03b5\u03c1\u03b3\u03b1\u03c3\u03af\u03b1\u03c2 \u03bc\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5\u03c2 \u0392\u03ad\u03c1\u03c4\u03b6\u03bf \u03ba\u03b1\u03b9 \u0396\u03ad\u03c1\u03b7  |url=http://www.aelfc.gr/index.php/anakoinoseis-menu/item/1239-lysi-tis-synergasias-me-tous-vertzo-kai-zeri|accessdate=2016-08-06}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nHe played the majority of his career in the [[Beta Ethniki|Beta]] and [[Gamma Ethniki]] championships. However, in 2011, his team [[Doxa Drama F.C.|Doxa Drama]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uefa.com/teamsandplayers/teams/club=2603728/domestic/ | title=Doxa Dramas squad |publisher=UEFA | accessdate=December 23, 2011}}</ref> was promoted to the [[Greek Superleague]] as a result of the [[Koriopolis]] scandal,<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/ellada/SuperLeague/sth_superleague_o_levadeiakos_kai_h_doksa_dramas.1421093.html | title=Doxa Dramas and Levadiakos to Superleague | publisher=Sport24 | date=October 22, 2011 | accessdate=October 22, 2011|language=el}}</ref> despite finishing third in the [[2010\u201311 Football League (Greece)#Promotion playoffs|promotion playoffs of the previous year]].\n\nOn January 7, 2014, Veria announced the return of Vertzos to the club as he signed a contract for one-and-a-half years.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://veriafc.gr/index.php/2012-10-10-16-25-23/541-o-a-vertzos-podosfairistis-tis-veroias |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107202326/http://veriafc.gr/index.php/2012-10-10-16-25-23/541-o-a-vertzos-podosfairistis-tis-veroias |archive-date=2014-01-07 |url-status=dead }}</ref> His contract expired on 31 June 2015 and it wasn't renewed. On 22 July 2015 he signed a two-year contract with AEL. A year later, on 6 August 2016, Vertzos left the club by mutual agreement. On 9 August 2016 he joined [[Trikala F.C.|Trikala]]. On 10 July 2017 he renewed his contract for another season.\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://archive.is/20130217170153/http://www.onsports.gr/onstats/soccer/player/877-Bertzos-Aggelos Onsports.gr profile] {{in lang|el}}\n* {{soccerway}}\n\n{{Trikala F.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vertzos, Angelos}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Greek footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:AE Larissa FC players]]\n[[Category:Acharnaikos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Paniliakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Proodeftiki F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Veria F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Doxa Drama F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Niki Volou FC players]]\n[[Category:Apollon Smyrni F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Superleague Greece players]]\n[[Category:Football League (Greece) players]]\n[[Category:Tri